# =============================================================================
# LDIF Test Scenarios — AcmeCorp
# Supplements acmecorp-5000-users.ldif with data designed to trigger:
#   1. Access Drift Detection (peer group anomalies)
#   2. SoD Violations (conflicting group memberships)
#   3. Integrity Check issues (broken refs, orphaned entries, empty groups)
#   4. Users in no groups
#   5. Missing profile/department group memberships
#   6. Disabled accounts still in sensitive groups
#
# Base DN: dc=acmecorp,dc=com
#
# IMPORTANT: If re-importing, run the cleanup first:
#   ldapmodify -x -D "cn=admin,dc=acmecorp,dc=com" -w <pw> -f acmecorp-test-cleanup.ldif
#   ldapdelete -x -D "cn=admin,dc=acmecorp,dc=com" -w <pw> -f acmecorp-test-cleanup-delete.txt
# Then load:
#   ldapmodify -x -D "cn=admin,dc=acmecorp,dc=com" -w <pw> -a -f acmecorp-test-scenarios.ldif
# =============================================================================


