# --- 3b. Orphaned entries — create temporary parent OUs, add entries,
#     then delete the parent OUs. This leaves the children orphaned.
#     NOTE: Not all LDAP servers allow deleting non-leaf entries.
#     If deletion fails, the OUs stay (entries are not orphaned) and the
#     orphaned-entry test must be skipped. ---

